00:38:42.101 --> 00:38:46.701
I said, “He’s doing something” and I
was just looking at her the way she was on

00:38:46.701 --> 00:38:47.701
Me.

00:38:47.701 --> 00:38:51.011
“My husband might be your husband’s boss”
this and that.

00:38:51.011 --> 00:38:54.841
I said, “Maybe I don’t know anything about
these things.

00:38:54.841 --> 00:38:57.811
I am sorry, I don’t know your list of people,
anything.

00:38:57.811 --> 00:38:59.591
I am not interested.”

00:38:59.591 --> 00:39:01.971
And then My husband came.

00:39:01.971 --> 00:39:03.751
So she said, “See that tall man.

00:39:03.751 --> 00:39:06.251
You know he’s very important.

00:39:06.251 --> 00:39:08.141
He’s with the Prime Minister.

00:39:08.141 --> 00:39:12.391
You go and talk to him and get Your husband
promoted.”

00:39:12.391 --> 00:39:23.721
I said ([Laughing] What is she up to?), I
said, “Sudhali, he is My husband.”

00:39:23.721 --> 00:39:24.721
“Heh!

00:39:24.721 --> 00:39:26.361
He’s your husband?

00:39:26.361 --> 00:39:27.361
Haan yaar!

00:39:27.361 --> 00:39:28.761
Oh my God!

00:39:28.761 --> 00:39:30.691
I am sorry I am.”

00:39:30.691 --> 00:39:32.861
I said, “It’s all right.”

00:39:32.861 --> 00:39:33.861
Common experience.

00:39:33.861 --> 00:39:42.441
The women also become IAS, you see, not actually
but as wives and I’ve been such a lost person

00:39:42.441 --> 00:39:44.501
with them.

00:39:44.501 --> 00:39:50.681
I could never understand what is there to
be IAS and to be his wife.

00:39:50.681 --> 00:39:52.481
It was beyond Me.

00:39:52.481 --> 00:39:59.021
But one thing, what really helped Me in all
this turmoil of life, because you know our

00:39:59.021 --> 00:40:09.701
pay is less, this, that all problems are there,
was the patriotism Raashtra Bhakti.

00:40:09.701 --> 00:40:11.761
My father was a great patriot.

00:40:11.761 --> 00:40:12.921
My mother was.

00:40:12.921 --> 00:40:17.911
They sacrificed everything for the independence
of this country.

00:40:17.911 --> 00:40:23.341
I cannot travel by any foreign airlines, whatever
maybe.

00:40:23.341 --> 00:40:26.041
Maybe Air India is not good, doesn’t matter.

00:40:26.041 --> 00:40:28.371
It’s My, My country’s.

00:40:28.371 --> 00:40:35.301
So the feeling that this is My country kept
Me going.

00:40:35.301 --> 00:40:39.231
You see you become like a Kargil soldier.

00:40:39.231 --> 00:40:42.211
You are fighting for your country.

00:40:42.211 --> 00:40:47.141
You are working for your country.

00:40:47.141 --> 00:40:50.401
My husband got into Indian Foreign Service.

00:40:50.401 --> 00:40:51.741
I told him, “Nothing doing.

00:40:51.741 --> 00:40:56.431
We don’t drink, both of us and I can’t
leave My country in the lurch at the time

00:40:56.431 --> 00:40:58.471
when we have got the freedom.

00:40:58.471 --> 00:41:00.921
So if you want you can go, I will not come.

00:41:00.921 --> 00:41:03.081
I don’t want to go to Foreign Service.”

00:41:03.081 --> 00:41:04.521
They cut his pay.

00:41:04.521 --> 00:41:07.331
That time, you know, 300 was a big amount.

00:41:07.331 --> 00:41:08.951
I said, “Doesn’t matter.

00:41:08.951 --> 00:41:10.971
Whatever it is, I’ll stay in My country.

00:41:10.971 --> 00:41:13.461
I’ll work in My country and you work here.

00:41:13.461 --> 00:41:15.971
I’ll support you every way.

00:41:15.971 --> 00:41:18.651
I don’t want anything.

00:41:18.651 --> 00:41:25.561
Nothing I want and you don’t take a bribe
at all otherwise that day I’ll leave this.”

00:41:25.561 --> 00:41:33.471
Otherwise also I said that, “The another
thing is our country has to develop.”

00:41:33.471 --> 00:41:36.481
Who will develop?

00:41:36.481 --> 00:41:41.031
I always felt that you are the spinal cord
of our country.

00:41:41.031 --> 00:41:43.241
You have to develop this country.

00:41:43.241 --> 00:41:44.241
What is this money?

00:41:44.241 --> 00:41:45.241
Comes and goes.

00:41:45.241 --> 00:41:50.621
You’ve seen the people who have got money,
where their children have gone?

00:41:50.621 --> 00:41:53.181
What has happened to them?

00:41:53.181 --> 00:41:54.181
What have they achieved?

00:41:54.181 --> 00:41:58.901
So I told very frankly that I will not go
to the Foreign Service of any kind because

00:41:58.901 --> 00:42:00.541
what is in the Foreign Service?

00:42:00.541 --> 00:42:06.581
I want to do everything in this country of
Mine for which I have also fought.

00:42:06.581 --> 00:42:13.971
I have fought a lot and this is what now sometimes,
you know, is disappointing to see what things

00:42:13.971 --> 00:42:15.061
are happening.

00:42:15.061 --> 00:42:16.421
But a day will come.

00:42:16.421 --> 00:42:18.211
This country will rise.

00:42:18.211 --> 00:42:19.211
How?

00:42:19.211 --> 00:42:24.771
Because when this happens, when this Kundalini
rising take place, when people become realized

00:42:24.771 --> 00:42:27.291
souls, they just transform.

00:42:27.291 --> 00:42:34.861
They become extremely patriotic, extremely
patriotic and they understand what is needed

00:42:34.861 --> 00:42:37.161
today for our country.

00:42:37.161 --> 00:42:39.101
They can sacrifice anything.

00:42:39.101 --> 00:42:48.061
They can live anywhere and they are not bothered
about some sort of a, you can call it a financial

00:42:48.061 --> 00:42:50.891
help or other material thing.

00:42:50.891 --> 00:42:53.151
They are above materialism.

00:42:53.151 --> 00:43:01.071
There are thousands and thousands like that
even in our country, thousands and also abroad.

00:43:01.071 --> 00:43:03.901
Now Sahaja Yoga is working 86 countries.

00:43:03.901 --> 00:43:13.031
They are all full of joy because with this
happening you get joy of a quality which has

00:43:13.031 --> 00:43:14.031
no double thing.

00:43:14.031 --> 00:43:15.311
It’s not happiness / unhappiness.

00:43:15.311 --> 00:43:22.541
It’s just joy and you have another thing
also with it, is the peace of mind.

00:43:22.541 --> 00:43:26.861
Just you are so peaceful, absolutely peaceful.

00:43:26.861 --> 00:43:31.401
You don’t have to worry about things.

00:43:31.401 --> 00:43:37.551
You don’t have to become jittery because
see the diseases you develop.

00:43:37.551 --> 00:43:41.871
Apart from that, all kinds of paralysis comes
on us.

00:43:41.871 --> 00:43:47.241
We had a doctor in our hospital there who
was working very hard.

00:43:47.241 --> 00:43:50.871
I told him that, “Doctor, see now your age
has come.

00:43:50.871 --> 00:43:52.381
You should take it easy.

00:43:52.381 --> 00:43:53.941
Daytime you must rest.

00:43:53.941 --> 00:43:55.111
There’s no need.

00:43:55.111 --> 00:43:59.161
You are not in a office, just rest, take rest
do something else.

00:43:59.161 --> 00:44:01.591
Read or you can go and play.

00:44:01.591 --> 00:44:02.591
Do something.”

00:44:02.591 --> 00:44:08.921
He wouldn’t listen to Me and then he got
paraplegia, means that failure of the hand

00:44:08.921 --> 00:44:10.551
and the leg, completely.

00:44:10.551 --> 00:44:11.821
He couldn’t even walk.

00:44:11.821 --> 00:44:13.971
He couldn’t lift his leg.

00:44:13.971 --> 00:44:16.131
Now he’s all right, cured.

00:44:16.131 --> 00:44:20.131
But then I told him that you take treatment
for your right side.

00:44:20.131 --> 00:44:21.911
That’s very important.

00:44:21.911 --> 00:44:27.531
It’s very simple treatment and which can
be done very easily.

