Now, whenever one has to die, one will die.

00:51:35.511 --> 00:51:39.721
But till then we are not bothered.

00:51:39.721 --> 00:51:45.491
Anything that you do will have a special light
of the Divine.

00:51:45.491 --> 00:51:51.701
I bless you from My heart that you develop
this subtle things within yourself and you

00:51:51.701 --> 00:51:56.231
try to understand that so far you have not
known yourself.

00:51:56.231 --> 00:51:57.561
